    <description>.NET for Android and MAUI bindings for the Android Java library 'androidx.fragment:fragment'.

Library description: The Support Library is a static library that you can add to your Android application in order to use APIs that are either not available for older platform versions or utility APIs that aren't a part of the framework APIs. Compatible on devices running API 14 or later.</description>
